About us

The Gym Pod

The Gym Pod is Singaporeâ€™s first 24/7, pay-per-use private gym. The Gym Pod also has other offerings such as The Flow Pod, The Grit Pod, The Rumble Pod and The Spin Pod. With a Smart Mirror, The Gym Pod provides workout videos to guide customers of beginner, intermediate and advanced levels to maximize their workout.

The gym is open 24 hours a day, 7 days a week (including public holidays!). We want to give you the liberty to exercise whenever you want! Psst night-shifters, now you work out at night.

Unlike the typical gym membership, The Gym Pod boasts its pay-per-use system so you'll never have to worry about wasting money on an annual gym membership. Even with our subscription plan, it is setup to give you discount for each session you choose to attend.

If you would like to know more, visit the official website at https://www.thegympod.com/

Gym Pod Experience

Gym Pod Experience is a platform created by the franchise owner of The Gym Pod @ 163 Bukit Merah Central. This blog is not the official website for The Gym Pod. We are here to improve your experience with our Pod and create a community here in Bukit Merah Central.

Bukit Merah Central has a community of healthy residents and hard-working professionals. The Gym Pod @ 163 Bukit Merah Central provides working professionals with an avenue to exercise before and after work, or even during their lunchtime. The private gym helps local residents achieve a healthier lifestyle.
